ygData.messageBody:
Kedge keep is lvl 30+. It's one of the hardest dungeons in the game.
There is a reason no one has explored it in depth. If you die in it,
you're gonna have a hell of a time getting back to your body. It's kind
of obvious that it holds some very kick ass items. The ones no one can
find anywhere.. but the people continue to leave kedge keep untouched.
And you're cleric won't do so hot in kedge. you need someone to cast a
water breathing spell on you. That or a fish bone earring.
